      "label": "业务使用层",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "a100000000000002",
      "type": "group",
      "x": 560,
      "y": -80,
      "width": 620,
      "height": 900,
      "label": "AI 陪练与技能编排层",
      "color": "6"
    },
    {
      "id": "a100000000000003",
      "type": "group",
      "x": 1240,
      "y": -80,
      "width": 760,
      "height": 900,
      "label": "RAG-Anything 知识服务层",
      "color": "4"
    },
    {
      "id": "a100000000000004",
      "type": "group",
      "x": 2060,
      "y": -80,
      "width": 620,
      "height": 900,
      "label": "外部模型与持久化",
      "color": "3"
    },
    {
      "id": "a100000000000005",
      "type": "group",
      "x": 1240,
      "y": 880,
      "width": 1440,
      "height": 380,
      "label": "迁移结论与残留风险",
      "color": "2"
    },
    {
      "id": "b100000000000001",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 0,
      "y": 0,
      "width": 420,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "# 用户入口\n\n销售/培训人员进入 AI 话术陪练前端，选择客户类型、产品、单位和沟通场景。",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "b100000000000002",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 0,
      "y": 180,
      "width": 420,
      "height": 140,
      "text": "# 话术陪练会话\n\n`ai-tutor-system` 负责创建会话、保存历史、接收用户发言，并把产品知识检索作为每轮回复的前置步骤。",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "b100000000000003",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 0,
      "y": 380,
      "width": 420,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "# 技能触发\n\n用户可触发 `peixun-skill` 或 `solution-generator-skill`，生成培训讲义、测试题、解决方案和 README。",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "b100000000000004",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 0,
      "y": 560,
      "width": 420,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "# 知识维护入口\n\n通过命令脚本或 REST API 导入文档、图片、Office、PDF、Markdown 等资料到指定知识库。",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "c100000000000001",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 620,
      "y": 0,
      "width": 480,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "# 场景与数据库解析\n\n`tutor_config.py` 将产品映射到知识库，例如“商务视频彩铃”映射到 `商务彩铃`。",
      "color": "6"
    },
    {
      "id": "c100000000000002",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 620,
      "y": 170,
      "width": 480,
      "height": 160,
      "text": "# 每轮 RAG 检索\n\n`tutor_backend.search_rag_knowledge()` 请求 `POST /ai_enhanced_search`，分别检索产品信息、销售话术、异议处理和评估标准。",
      "color": "6"
    },
    {
      "id": "c100000000000003",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 620,
      "y": 380,
      "width": 480,
      "height": 140,
      "text": "# Prompt 组装\n\n把场景、客户角色、对话历史和 RAG 返回内容组装成系统提示词，约束 AI 不编造产品知识。",
      "color": "6"
    },
    {
      "id": "c100000000000004",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 620,
      "y": 570,
      "width": 480,
      "height": 130,
      "text": "# 技能流水线\n\n`run_skill_pipeline_once.py` 读取配置，调用合规生成套件，并通过 8003 RAG 服务补充业务上下文。",
      "color": "6"
    },
    {
      "id": "d100000000000001",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1300,
      "y": 0,
      "width": 520,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "# FastAPI 统一入口\n\n`rag-anything-api/app.py` 暴露 `/search`、`/ai_enhanced_search`、`/query`、`/ingest/path`、`/db/*` 等兼容接口。",
      "color": "4"
    },
    {
      "id": "d100000000000002",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1300,
      "y": 170,
      "width": 520,
      "height": 150,
      "text": "# RAGAnythingService\n\n负责按 database 获取 RAG-Anything 实例、初始化 LightRAG 存储、执行查询和文件入库。",
      "color": "4"
    },
    {
      "id": "d100000000000003",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1300,
      "y": 370,
      "width": 520,
      "height": 130,
      "text": "# 查询分支\n\n有 database 时查指定库；无 database 时遍历注册表执行多库查询。默认 query mode 来自 `DEFAULT_QUERY_MODE`。",
      "color": "4"
    },
    {
      "id": "d100000000000004",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1300,
      "y": 550,
      "width": 520,
      "height": 130,
      "text": "# 入库分支\n\n`/ingest/path` 或 `import_files.py` 收集支持格式文件，调用 `process_document_complete()` 进入 RAG-Anything 官方解析与索引流程。",
      "color": "4"
    },
    {
      "id": "d100000000000005",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1300,
      "y": 720,
      "width": 520,
      "height": 80,
      "text": "# 兼容响应\n\n返回旧接口字段：`query`、`results`、`total_found`、`database`、`context`、`sources`。",
      "color": "4"
    },
    {
      "id": "e100000000000001",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2100,
      "y": 0,
      "width": 500,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "# MiniMax LLM\n\n陪练对话、评估报告、RAG-Anything 查询生成和知识图谱构建主要使用 MiniMax 模型。",
      "color": "3"
    },
    {
      "id": "e100000000000002",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2100,
      "y": 170,
      "width": 500,
      "height": 110,
      "text": "# 硅基流动 Embedding\n\nRAG-Anything/LightRAG 通过 OpenAI 兼容接口调用 `BAAI/bge-m3` 向量模型。",
      "color": "3"
    },
    {
      "id": "e100000000000003",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2100,
      "y": 330,
      "width": 500,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "# MinerU 解析\n\n复杂文档、图片和版面内容通过 MinerU 解析，输出 Markdown、content list、layout 等中间产物。",
      "color": "3"
    },
    {
      "id": "e100000000000004",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2100,
      "y": 500,
      "width": 500,
      "height": 140,
      "text": "# RAG-Anything 存储\n\n主存储在 `rag-anything-api/storage/raganything/{database}/rag_storage`，包含 KV、向量库和图谱关系文件。",
      "color": "3"
    },
    {
      "id": "e100000000000005",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2100,
      "y": 700,
      "width": 500,
      "height": 100,
      "text": "# 业务输出\n\n会话 JSON、培训材料、考题、解决方案、README、自检报告分别落到 `tutor_data`、`training_output`、`solution_output`。",
      "color": "3"
    },
    {
      "id": "f100000000000001",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1300,
      "y": 950,
      "width": 560,
      "height": 150,
      "text": "# 迁移判断\n\n主运行链路和迁移导入链路已经迁移到 `RAGAnything + MinerU + LightRAG`：陪练、技能流水线、查询脚本、入库脚本和迁移脚本都通过统一服务层。",
      "color": "4"
    },
    {
      "id": "f100000000000002",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1920,
      "y": 950,
      "width": 620,
      "height": 150,
      "text": "# 非运行残留\n\n可执行 Python 路径已清理旧直连栈。仍保留的是历史文档中的旧 Chroma/旧处理器说明，以及 `storage/lightrag` legacy 兼容目录；这些不再属于主运行链路。",
      "color": "2"
    }
  ],
